name: SPE Meta-analysis Datasets
description: This is a datasets for SPE(Self-prioritization effect) Meta-analysis

variableMeasured.name: Article_coding
variableMeasured.description: The ariticle code associated with the research.

variableMeasured.name: Coder
variableMeasured.description: The coder(s) responsible for data collection or analysis.

variableMeasured.name: Author
variableMeasured.description: The author(s) of the article.

variableMeasured.name: Author_email
variableMeasured.description: The email address of the author(s).

variableMeasured.name: Year
variableMeasured.description: The year of publication of the article.

variableMeasured.name: Journal
variableMeasured.description: The journal in which the article was published.

variableMeasured.name: Study
variableMeasured.description: The name or identifier of the study.

variableMeasured.name: Language_article
variableMeasured.description: The language of the article.

variableMeasured.name: Language_experiment
variableMeasured.description: The language used in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Keywords
variableMeasured.description: Keywords associated with the study.

variableMeasured.name: Research_topic
variableMeasured.description: The topic or area of research to which the study belongs.

variableMeasured.name: Target_effect
variableMeasured.description: The specific effect or phenomenon being investigated in the study.

variableMeasured.name: Ind_var_I_Matchness
variableMeasured.description: The level of matchness for independent variable I in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Ind_var_II_Target_words
variableMeasured.description: The target words(labels) used for independent variable II in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Ind_var_III
variableMeasured.description: The optinal manipulation of independent variable III in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Experimetnal_design
variableMeasured.description: The experimental design used in the study, e.g., within, between and mixed.

variableMeasured.name: Deviations_exp_design
variableMeasured.description: Any deviations or modifications from the original experimental design.

variableMeasured.name: Subject_recruitment
variableMeasured.description: The method or process used for subject recruitment in the study.

variableMeasured.name: Education
variableMeasured.description: The level of education of participants.

variableMeasured.name: Sample_size
variableMeasured.description: The size of the sample or number of participants in the study.

variableMeasured.name: Female
variableMeasured.description: The number of female participants in the study.

variableMeasured.name: Mean_age
variableMeasured.description: The mean age of the participants in the study.

variableMeasured.name: SD_age
variableMeasured.description: The standard deviation of the age of the participants in the study.

variableMeasured.name: Environment
variableMeasured.description: The environment or setting in which the experiment took place.

variableMeasured.name: Practice
variableMeasured.description: Whether practice trials were included in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Practice_pass
variableMeasured.description: Conditions for determining participants to pass the practice test.

variableMeasured.name: Practice_trials
variableMeasured.description: The number of practice trials in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Formal_trials
variableMeasured.description: The number of formal trials in the experiment.

variableMeasured.name: Formal_blocks
variableMeasured.description: The number of formal blocks in the experiment.
